'''利斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Leith'''}}，{{IPAc-en|ˈ|l|iː|θ}} {{respell|LEETH|<nowiki>'</nowiki>}}）是[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]][[愛丁堡|愛丁堡]]北部的一個地區，1920年併入[[愛丁堡|愛丁堡]]市之前是一個自治市，處在[[利斯河_(蘇格蘭)|利斯河]]口。<ref name=hist>{{Cite web |url=http://www.electricscotland.com/history/leith/33.htm |title=The Story of Leith XXXIII. How Leith was Governed |accessdate=2014-01-21 |archive-date=2007-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070310175246/http://www.electricscotland.com/history/leith/33.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref> 歷史上利斯長期作為作為愛丁堡的港口存在。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.scottish-places.info/features/featurefirst7845.html |title=Overview of Port of Leith |author= |date= |work=[[Gazetteer_for_Scotland|Gazetteer for Scotland]] |accessdate=6 March 2012 |archive-date=2014-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203071228/http://www.scottish-places.info/features/featurefirst7845.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

利斯這一地名首次出現於[[荷里路德修道院|荷里路德修道院]]的予建特許狀中，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://canmore.rcahms.gov.uk/en/site/51962/details/edinburgh+leith+general/ |title=Site Record for Edinburgh, Leith, General North Leith; South Leith Details (Canmore) |author= |date= |work= |publisher=RCAHMS |accessdate=6 March 2012 |archive-date=2014-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203233425/http://canmore.rcahms.gov.uk/en/site/51962/details/edinburgh+leith+general/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{sfn|Campbell|1827|p=2}} 1329年被官方確認為愛丁堡的港口，當時[[羅伯特·布魯斯|羅伯特一世]]控制著蘇格蘭。現在依然是繁忙的港口，2003年年吞吐貨物150萬噸。<ref>Figure for 2003; {{cite press release
